From b628d9dc3b9f8563ae801a1a7fe448cf177a254a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Risheek Shrestha <risheek@example.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 22:54:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(ui): polish all tsx pages with Tailwind, no logic
 changes

- Restyle stub/unstyled pages (Jobs, JobDetails, ApplyForJob, MyResumes,
  UploadResume, MyApplications, NotFound, Profile) to match the existing
  dark slate/cyan design system used by Navbar, Dashboard and Index.
- Restyle all admin pages (AdminDashboard, AdminJobs, Applications,
  AcceptedApplications, CreateJob, EditJobs) with cards, badges and
  consistent form styling.
- Reconcile ResumeScore's light/teal theme into the app's dark theme.
- Add reusable EmptyState and Pagination UI components.
- Load Space Grotesk + Inter fonts referenced by the existing
  .font-display utility, which previously had no font-face loaded.
- No component logic, state, handlers, effects, or API calls were
  changed; only JSX markup and className strings.
